Achievements.Name: Upload And Share
Achievements.Description: Upload a 2K Share file to the 2K Sports server.

Achievements.Name: Online Ranked Win
Achievements.Description: Play and finish an online Ranked Match and win.

Achievements.Name: 30 Online Ranked Wins
Achievements.Description: Accumulate 30 Online Ranked Match wins.

Achievements.Name: Pontiac (Online)
Achievements.Description: Qualify for the Pontiac Virtual NCAA® Final 4® and complete at least one game in the tournament.

Achievements.Name: Drills Medal
Achievements.Description: Earn Gold in any of the drills in the All-American Training Challenge - Singles mode.

Achievements.Name: Beat Oden
Achievements.Description: Beat Greg Oden at all of his drills in All-American Training Challenge - CPU Duel mode.

Achievements.Name: Drills Domination
Achievements.Description: Beat all of the opponents in All-American Training Challenge - CPU Duel mode.

Achievements.Name: Isomotion Training
Achievements.Description: Successfully perform any of the Isomotion moves in Tutorial mode.

Achievements.Name: ABL Win
Achievements.Description: Play and win an ABL game in Open or Career Legacy.

Achievements.Name: Over .500
Achievements.Description: Finish a season in Career Legacy with a winning record.

Achievements.Name: Fan Support
Achievements.Description: Finish a season in Career Legacy with at least 90% Average Attendance.

Achievements.Name: Top Recruit
Achievements.Description: Sign a recruit ranked Top 10 in the nation in Career Legacy.

Achievements.Name: Job Offer
Achievements.Description: Receive a coaching job offer from a school in a Power Conference in Career Legacy.

Achievements.Name: Conference Champion
Achievements.Description: Win a conference tournament championship in Career Legacy.

Achievements.Name: National Champion
Achievements.Description: Win a National Championship in Legacy mode (Open or Career).

Achievements.Name: Play Designer
Achievements.Description: Create and Save a custom Playbook using Play Designer.

Achievements.Name: Custom Chants
Achievements.Description: Create and save a custom Chant using Chant Creator.

Achievements.Name: Buzzer Beater
Achievements.Description: Win a game with a buzzer beater shot.

Achievements.Name: At The Line
Achievements.Description: Shoot over 85% from the FT line with any team.  Minimum of 15 FT attempts.

Achievements.Name: Glass Domination
Achievements.Description: Out rebound the opponent by at least 15 with any team.

Achievements.Name: On Fire
Achievements.Description: Make 5 consecutive 3PT shots in a game with any team.

Achievements.Name: Comeback
Achievements.Description: Start the 2nd half down by at least 15 points and win the game with any team.

Achievements.Name: Swat Team
Achievements.Description: Block at least 10 shots with any team.

Achievements.Name: Defense
Achievements.Description: Hold the opponent to 35% shooting or below with any team.

Achievements.Name: Double Double
Achievements.Description: Get a double-double with any player.

Achievements.Name: Triple Double
Achievements.Description: Get a triple-double with any player.

Achievements.Name: '07 Ohio State vs Florida
Achievements.Description: Win this 2007 Championship matchup as either '07 Ohio State or '07 Florida.  MOP difficulty.

Achievements.Name: '79 Indiana St vs Michigan St
Achievements.Description: Win this 1979 Championship matchup as either '79 Indiana State or '79 Michigan St.  MOP difficulty.

Achievements.Name: '88 Kansas vs Oklahoma
Achievements.Description: Win this 1988 Championship matchup as either '88 Kansas or '88 Oklahoma.  MOP difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Pontiac Tournament (Offline)
Achievements.Description: Complete and win a Pontiac NCAA® Tournament. Must play all games as the same school w/o simulating.
